documentation.text:
@dev Tokens Used:
 {wbnb, busd} - Required for liquidity routing when doing swaps.
 {rewardToken} - Token generated by staking our funds.
 {brew} - BREW token to buy and burn.
 {lpPair} - Token that the strategy maximizes. The same token that users deposit in the vault.
 {lpToken0, lpToken1} - Tokens that the strategy maximizes. IUniswapV2Pair tokens

@dev Third Party Contracts:
 {unirouter} - CafeSwap unirouter
 {masterchef} - MasterChef contract
 {poolId} - MasterChef pool id

@dev Distribution of fees earned. This allocations relative to the % implemented on doSplit().
 Current implementation separates 2.5% for fees.
 {BURN_FEE} - 1.5% goes to buying BREW and burning it.
 {CALL_FEE} - 0.5% goes to whoever executes the harvest function as gas subsidy.
 {STRATEGIST_FEE} - 0.5% goes to the strategist.
 {MAX_FEE} - Aux const used to safely calc the correct amounts.
 {WITHDRAWAL_FEE} - Fee taxed when a user withdraws funds. 10 === 0.1% fee.
 {WITHDRAWAL_MAX} - Aux const used to safely calc the correct amounts.

@dev Routes we take to swap tokens using PancakeSwap.
 {rewardTokenToWbnbRoute} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {wbnb}.
 {wbnbToBrewRoute} - Route we take to get from {wbnb} into {brew}.
 {rewardTokenToLp0Route} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {lpToken0}.
 {rewardTokenToLp1Route} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {lpToken1}.
@dev Event that is fired each time someone harvests the strat.
@dev Initializes the strategy with the token to maximize.

@dev Takes out 2.5% as system fees from the rewards. 
 0.5% -> Call Fee
 0.5% -> Strategist fee
 1.5% -> BURN BREW
@dev Swaps {rewardToken} for {lpToken0}, {lpToken1} & {wbnb} using PancakeSwap.

@dev Function to calculate the total underlaying {lpPair} held by the strat.
 It takes into account both the funds in hand, as the funds allocated in the MasterChef.
@dev It calculates how much {lpPair} the contract holds.
@dev It calculates how much {lpPair} the strategy has allocated in the MasterChef

@dev Function that has to be called as part of strat migration. It sends all the available funds back to the 
 vault, ready to be migrated to the new strat.
@dev Pauses deposits. Withdraws all funds from the MasterChef, leaving rewards behind
@dev Pauses the strat.
@dev Unpauses the strat.

@dev Updates address where strategist fee earnings will go.
 @param _strategist new strategist address.

devdoc.details: Implementation of a strategy to get yields from farming LP Pools in CafeSwap. This strat is currently compatible with all LP pools.

StratHarvest(address).details: Event that is fired each time someone harvests the strat.

balanceOf().details: Function to calculate the total underlaying {lpPair} held by the strat. It takes into account both the funds in hand, as the funds allocated in the MasterChef.

balanceOfLpPair().details: It calculates how much {lpPair} the contract holds.

balanceOfPool().details: It calculates how much {lpPair} the strategy has allocated in the MasterChef

constructor.details: Initializes the strategy with the token to maximize.

deposit().details: Function that puts the funds to work. It gets called whenever someone deposits in the strategy's vault contract. It deposits {lpPair} in the MasterChef to farm {rewardToken}

harvest().details: Core function of the strat, in charge of collecting and re-investing rewards. 1. It claims rewards from the MasterChef. 2. It charges the system fees to simplify the split. 3. It swaps the {rewardToken} token for {lpToken0} & {lpToken1} 4. Adds more liquidity to the pool. 5. It deposits the new LP tokens.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

panic().details: Pauses deposits. Withdraws all funds from the MasterChef, leaving rewards behind

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

retireStrat().details: Function that has to be called as part of strat migration. It sends all the available funds back to the  vault, ready to be migrated to the new strat.

setStrategist(address).details: Updates address where strategist fee earnings will go.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdraw(uint256).details: Withdraws funds and sends them back to the vault. It withdraws {lpPair} from the MasterChef. The available {lpPair} minus fees is returned to the vault.

BURN_FEE.details: Distribution of fees earned. This allocations relative to the % implemented on doSplit(). Current implementation separates 2.5% for fees. {BURN_FEE} - 1.5% goes to buying BREW and burning it. {CALL_FEE} - 0.5% goes to whoever executes the harvest function as gas subsidy. {STRATEGIST_FEE} - 0.5% goes to the strategist. {MAX_FEE} - Aux const used to safely calc the correct amounts. {WITHDRAWAL_FEE} - Fee taxed when a user withdraws funds. 10 === 0.1% fee. {WITHDRAWAL_MAX} - Aux const used to safely calc the correct amounts.

rewardTokenToWbnbRoute.details: Routes we take to swap tokens using PancakeSwap. {rewardTokenToWbnbRoute} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {wbnb}. {wbnbToBrewRoute} - Route we take to get from {wbnb} into {brew}. {rewardTokenToLp0Route} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {lpToken0}. {rewardTokenToLp1Route} - Route we take to get from {rewardToken} into {lpToken1}.

unirouter.details: Third Party Contracts: {unirouter} - CafeSwap unirouter {masterchef} - MasterChef contract {poolId} - MasterChef pool id

vault.details: Coffee Contracts: {vault} - Address of the vault that controls the strategy's funds. {strategist} - Address of the strategy author/deployer where strategist fee will go.
